            "body": "Ooh, thanks @matusvalo. Gonna post PR soon.\n\n> Thank you for your effort. I like new theme. Question: is it possible to port banner to new theme too?\n\nDo you mean this banner?\n\n<img width=\"2962\" height=\"476\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/fd1fd533-52bb-4409-998b-f3e24b1cec49\" />\n\nI have already ported it to this:\n\n<img width=\"2962\" height=\"476\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/14b29a31-5344-46d4-915a-18a9f06d70c0\" />\n\n(I have changed the wording a bit, but the text is customizable with a single option in the documentation `conf.py`.)",
