        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "> Looking at [flintlib/flint#2575](https://github.com/flintlib/flint/pull/2575) there may be license issues? (I don't know if that still applies?)\n\nThey don't apply anymore. It's regular MIT. Historically, at the very beginning, I have chosen weird proprietary license. I have changed the license to dual-licensing, allowing companies to purchase it under a paid license to receive priority support and legal compliance.",
